Comment: 0,0:01:27.06,0:01:29.44,saint tail op jp,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:87066,89444}{\blur1}want you here tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.70,0:00:21.66,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:17705,21668}Whenever my feelings were hurt,\NI couldn't see anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.66,0:00:25.58,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:21668,25588}because I held a lie in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.58,0:00:29.55,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:25588,29551}Time moved faster than I could react,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.55,0:00:34.59,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:29551,34597}so I pulled myself away\Nfrom everything, but now
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.59,0:00:40.64,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:34597,40645}I can't stop anything at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.06,0:00:47.61,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:41062,47610}Accepting everything, I rise up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.57,0:00:53.49,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:49571,53491}I'll fly over all of time\Nwhile holding onto your presence,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:56.99,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:53491,56995}following the trace of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.99,0:01:03.00,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:56995,63001}My world becomes engulfed with light.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.46,0:01:09.25,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:65461,69257}A never ending sky,\Nyour never changing eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.25,0:01:12.96,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:69257,72969}I want to love these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.96,0:01:19.35,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:72969,79350}No matter the distance,\Nor if we are separated
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.35,0:01:22.77,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:79350,82770}we are always connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.06,0:01:29.44,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:87066,89444}Want you here tonight!
Comment: 0,0:01:31.11,0:01:31.11,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:91112,91112}Part A
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.90,0:01:38.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:94907,98536}There's this boy I'd like to meet,\Nnamed Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.53,0:01:40.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:98536,100288}Is he in this school?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.04,0:01:48.67,saint tail default,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:106044,108671}A First Rendezvous of Tears?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.92,0:01:56.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:114927,116971}I've finally found you!\NAsuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.76,0:02:02.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:120767,122101}All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.68,0:02:04.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:122685,124937}H… hey, what are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.93,0:02:07.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:124937,127065}I looked all over town for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.10,0:02:10.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:128107,130026}But what are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.36,0:02:12.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:130360,132987}It took so long to find you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.65,0:02:17.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:133655,137283}I guess I couldn't find you,\Nsince you're so small.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.28,0:02:20.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:137283,140453}Answer my question,\Nbefore this turns into a fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.57,0:02:23.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:141579,143831}Meimi, who is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.83,0:02:25.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:143831,145333}She's a new student!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.33,0:02:27.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:145333,147293}I'll tell you about her later!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.25,0:02:31.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:148252,151673}I guess she doesn't need me\Nto take care of her!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.29,0:02:33.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:152298,153675}{\i1}Some nerve!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:35.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:154509,155468}Humph!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.84,0:02:40.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:158846,160056}Cute… cute…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.05,0:02:41.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:160056,161599}Knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.59,0:02:43.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:161599,163643}Relax. It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.26,0:02:46.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:164268,166104}{\i1}What is with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.64,0:02:53.82,saint tail sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:169649,173820}Rina Takamiya
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.23,0:02:53.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:170233,173820}I'm Rina Takamiya, a new student.\NNice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.28,0:03:00.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:178282,180743}Asuka, why don't you\Nshow me around?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.74,0:03:01.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:180743,181994}Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.99,0:03:05.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:181994,185581}Why not?! You should be\Nnice to new students.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:08.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:185581,188126}She's cool, I like tall girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.12,0:03:10.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:188126,190211}She doesn't look 14.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.21,0:03:12.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:190211,192088}She's got a nice figure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.08,0:03:13.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:192088,193715}Maybe she's a model, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.25,0:03:17.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:194257,197510}Stop! You over there!\NDon't go making assumptions!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.51,0:03:18.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:197510,198928}She heard us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.26,0:03:24.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:200263,204392}When I grow up, I'm going to\Nbecome a police officer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.14,0:03:26.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:205143,206394}A police officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.72,0:03:29.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:206728,209856}That's right.\NI'm going to catch bad guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.64,0:03:36.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:211649,216028}Especially that sneaky thief,\NSt. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.02,0:03:38.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:216028,218072}I'm going to arrest her with\Nmy bare hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.49,0:03:41.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:220491,221868}Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.86,0:03:44.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:221868,224579}I'm the one who's going\Nto arrest her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.57,0:03:51.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:224579,231419}Well, Ms. Takamiya, Asuka Jr. was appointed\Nby the mayor to investigate St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:55.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:233087,235298}Well, the Mayor happens\Nto be my Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.29,0:03:59.30,saint tail sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:235298,239302}{\an8}The Mayor's Niece
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.09,0:04:03.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:240094,243014}That's right?\NIs… that… right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.80,0:04:06.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:243806,246976}Then I'll go right over and ask\Nmy Uncle for permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.81,0:04:10.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:247810,250021}{\i1}There's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.02,0:04:13.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:250021,253191}{\i1}St. Tail won't be captured\Nthat easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.23,0:04:15.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:254233,255193}{\i1}Meimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.19,0:04:16.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:255193,256903}{\i1}Poor thing, you're trembling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.61,0:04:19.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:257612,259864}What's with her,\Nsticking so close to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:23.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:260114,263284}Humph! Suit yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.28,0:04:23.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:263284,263951}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.24,0:04:30.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:269248,270792}Ancient Hidden\NTreasures Exhibition?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:35.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:271375,275171}Yes, it's being held now\Nat the Central Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.17,0:04:36.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:275171,276589}The problem is…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.58,0:04:39.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:276589,279008}The "Dagger of Yatto"\Nthat's on display…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.59,0:04:42.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:279592,282011}It's not what it seems to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.01,0:04:43.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:282011,283971}It's not a hidden treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.34,0:04:45.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:284347,285223}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:47.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:285681,287266}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.26,0:04:50.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:287266,290561}The dagger is a copy that I made.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.56,0:04:52.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:290561,292438}It's a replica!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.64,0:04:56.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:292647,296150}Replica… you mean it's a fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.60,0:05:00.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:296609,300446}I usually work as a sculptor…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.44,0:05:04.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:300446,304659}But one day, I was asked by the man\Nin charge of Central Hall, Mr. Mizutani
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:08.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:304659,308120}to make a replica of the\NDagger of Yatto.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.91,0:05:14.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:308913,314001}I made it because he promised me that\Nhe was only going to use it
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.00,0:05:17.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:314001,317296}as a decoration\Nin his house, just to enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.29,0:05:20.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:317296,320174}I never thought he would exhibit it\Nas the real Dagger of Yatto!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:24.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:321008,324929}If I report it to the police,\NI'll probably be arrested, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:30.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:324929,330309}I can't sleep at night because I think\Nabout everybody I'm deceiving.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:31.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:330309,331894}What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.10,0:05:40.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:338109,340903}The Lord will surely forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.90,0:05:43.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:340903,343531}After all, you've confessed\Nand repented.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.78,0:05:45.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:344782,345992}Sister…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.53,0:05:50.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:346534,350621}Don't worry. I'm sure the Lord\Nwill guide you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.46,0:06:00.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:357461,360131}So that's the story, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.63,0:06:02.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:360631,362133}Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.13,0:06:04.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:362133,364886}I don't know much\Nabout ancient relics,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.88,0:06:08.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:364886,368598}whether it's Jomon period earthenware,\Na burial mound figure, or a clay doll,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.59,0:06:10.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:368598,370975}you can count on\NSt. Tail to recover it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.22,0:06:12.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:371225,372560}Meimi…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.56,0:06:14.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:372560,374186}It's a dagger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.72,0:06:19.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:374729,379317}I've got an idea of how things are\Nbetween you and Ms. Takamiya,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.31,0:06:20.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:379317,380359}but try to stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.40,0:06:25.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:383404,385364}I'll show her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.91,0:06:35.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:393915,395207}I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.25,0:06:37.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:396250,397418}Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.83,0:06:42.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:397835,402632}Meimi, I'm quite sure my magic\Ntrick will work this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.63,0:06:44.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:402632,404008}Want to see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:49.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:404008,409221}Not right now. But, could I\Nborrow one of your magic tricks?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.38,0:06:52.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:410389,412183}One of my magic tricks?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.14,0:07:02.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:419148,422860}I'm going to send him a warning\Nthat will blow his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.15,0:07:09.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:426155,429533}Asuka!\NCan I eat lunch with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.91,0:07:15.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:430910,435581}No way!\NGirls always want to trade snacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.58,0:07:17.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:435581,437792}I'm not interested in doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.54,0:07:22.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:441545,442296}What's this…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.92,0:07:29.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:444924,449637}"I'm going to Central Hall tonight\Nto get the Dagger of Yatto. – St. Tail"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.93,0:07:35.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:450930,455059}For a thief, she sure does send\Nlovely warnings.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.05,0:07:35.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:455059,455977}Doesn't she Asuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.97,0:07:37.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:455977,457311}Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.31,0:07:38.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:457311,458396}What was that noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.39,0:07:39.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:458396,459855}What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.98,0:07:44.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:461983,464568}It's a warning from St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.56,0:07:45.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:464568,465569}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.56,0:07:47.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:465569,467154}Let me taste some, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.57,0:07:50.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:468572,470992}Hey don't eat it!\NIt's my lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.45,0:07:53.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:471450,473911}What are you talking about?\NDon't hog it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.91,0:07:57.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:473911,477289}{\an8}– Hey don't eat my hand!\N– Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.37,0:07:57.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:474370,477289}What is with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.91,0:07:59.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:477915,479500}Your chopsticks broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.50,0:08:01.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:479500,481627}Yes, it seems so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.80,0:08:12.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:489802,492471}I've been waiting for you, Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.47,0:08:15.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:492471,495975}My name is Mizutani and I'm the\None in charge of this exhibition.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.55,0:08:18.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:496559,498310}Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.31,0:08:20.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:498310,500479}The pleasure is mine, Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.47,0:08:22.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:500479,502815}Let's get down to business.\NMay I see the Dagger of Yatto?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.81,0:08:23.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:502815,503858}Please follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.15,0:08:36.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:512158,516495}It's almost like a movie set.\NAll this just for the exhibition?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.49,0:08:42.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:516495,522460}Yes, I even have a special exhibition\Nroom just for the Dagger of Yatto.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.46,0:08:43.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:522460,523377}This way please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.21,0:08:54.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:528215,534555}It's inside this pyramid set.\NWe've set up a room in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.39,0:09:01.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:538392,541979}If the dagger is stolen and\Nthere's an investigation…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.36,0:09:17.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:553365,557119}The cameras are on 24 hours a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.53,0:09:18.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:557536,558788}Asuka Jr.?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.78,0:09:24.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:558788,564335}Are there any particular orders\Nyou have for the guards on duty?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.33,0:09:28.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:564335,568380}Shall we guard it\Nfrom inside the room?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.38,0:09:32.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:568380,572134}No… just guard the entrance\Nof the exhibition hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.13,0:09:33.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:572134,573260}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:40.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:577014,580476}I'll hide inside that Sarcophagus,\Nif it's okay with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.47,0:09:41.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:580476,581477}Huh? Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.56,0:09:47.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:582561,587942}St. Tail usually appears from above.\NSo this should give me a good view.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:51.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:588901,591403}We'll make her think this place\Nis not heavily guarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.40,0:09:55.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:591403,595366}When she comes in here…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.36,0:09:57.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:595366,597451}I'll catch her in the act and\Narrest her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.70,0:10:01.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:599703,601413}This set is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.41,0:10:03.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:601413,603541}The place is narrow, so I'll get\Nher for sure this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.04,0:10:06.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:604041,606502}Not clever enough, Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.87,0:10:08.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:606877,608045}Takamiya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.88,0:10:14.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:611882,614260}You've got to trap her\Nmore aggressively.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.26,0:10:16.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:614260,616387}It's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.38,0:10:17.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:616387,617680}You're bothering me,\Nso go on home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.18,0:10:21.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:618180,621016}Hmm… You really mean that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.43,0:10:24.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:623435,624645}Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.18,0:10:26.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:625187,626355}"To Asuka Jr."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.35,0:10:30.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:626355,630151}"Please look after my niece, Rina.\NI'm sure she'll be able to help you."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.15,0:10:31.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:630151,631819}"Please let her assist you."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.81,0:10:33.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:631819,633821}"– Mayor Hideo Morinaka"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.78,0:10:42.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:636782,642830}I'll be in the surveillance room,\Nwatching for your strategy to fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.79,0:10:45.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:644790,645624}Darn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:50.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:645624,650504}But with my strategy, tonight will be\Nthe last night for St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.92,0:10:52.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:650921,652715}Who said that you could…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.71,0:10:53.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:652715,653674}Read… Read…
Comment: 0,0:11:00.68,0:11:00.68,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:660681,660681}Eyecatch A
Comment: 0,0:11:06.68,0:11:06.68,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:666687,666687}Eyecatch B
Comment: 0,0:11:11.69,0:11:11.69,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:671692,671692}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.33,0:11:29.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:685331,689126}Forgive me, for I use\Nno gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.00,0:11:35.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:694006,695132}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.38,0:11:38.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:697384,698802}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.63,0:11:42.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:700638,702306}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.41,0:12:06.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:725412,726830}Be careful…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.83,0:12:08.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:726830,728624}Especially for Ms. Takamiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.71,0:12:16.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:732711,736590}May the blessings of God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.43,0:12:29.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:744431,749436}I won't lose tonight's fight.\NThey will see my victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.45,0:12:52.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:770457,772668}They're only guarding the entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.66,0:12:56.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:772668,776046}That's pretty lenient, considering\Nthey're up against St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.34,0:13:03.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:782344,783178}There.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.35,0:13:13.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:791353,793439}So that's the Dagger of Yatto.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.60,0:13:19.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:796608,799403}It's Show Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.41,0:13:28.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:806410,808579}Rina, the security camera!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.24,0:13:30.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:809246,810331}What did you say!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.62,0:13:37.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:814626,817004}How could this happen at\Nsuch a critical moment?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.00,0:13:39.00,saint tail sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:817004,819006}Please Stand By
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.13,0:13:47.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:825137,827431}{\i1}She's here… St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.18,0:13:53.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:830184,833812}{\i1}That's right, as soon as you touch\Nthat case, you're finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.48,0:14:00.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:838484,840569}Wait a moment, Rina!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.56,0:14:02.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:840569,842905}{\i1}She's got to be kidding,\Nnot taking us seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.90,0:14:05.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:842905,845699}{\i1}I can't count on Asuka's strategy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.78,0:14:10.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:848786,850996}Set target: Inside the pyramid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.83,0:14:17.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:856835,857836}Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.67,0:14:20.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:858670,860672}That's as far as you go, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.38,0:14:30.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:867388,870474}Asuka, it'll all be over in a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.06,0:14:39.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:877064,879233}Let me see your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.40,0:14:42.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:881402,882027}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.57,0:14:50.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:888575,890786}What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.62,0:15:00.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:899628,900754}Damn…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.39,0:15:15.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:912391,915561}There, now the gas will fill the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.56,0:15:17.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:915561,917938}You can't escape now, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:35.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:932494,935664}Try not to… breathe in…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:37.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:935664,937791}…as much as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:42.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:940294,942296}{\i1}He'll see my face!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.25,0:15:46.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:943255,946216}{\i1}I've got to get out of here!\NTake it easy, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.21,0:15:48.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:946216,948260}{\i1}But… I can't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.55,0:15:51.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:949553,951513}{\i1}Aren't you going to flee, St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.18,0:15:54.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:952181,954099}{\i1}Maybe I'll get to see your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.31,0:15:59.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:956310,959646}{\i1}It's no use… I can't run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.77,0:16:02.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:960772,962399}St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.39,0:16:03.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:962399,963525}Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.48,0:16:11.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:968489,971700}My eyes are so teary, I can't see!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.07,0:16:16.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:975078,976246}I can't see!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.49,0:16:18.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:976497,978707}{\i1}Tear gas?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.08,0:16:23.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:981084,983170}It should have worked by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.21,0:16:29.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:987216,989384}What the hell is he doing with her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.80,0:16:40.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:997809,1000270}St. Tail!\NWhere is St. Tail!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.89,0:16:44.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1000896,1004399}There couldn't have been a better opportunity\Nto catch her! What were you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.39,0:16:48.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1004399,1008612}Idiot! "What were you doing!"\Nis something I should be asking you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.61,0:16:51.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1008612,1011073}I thought I was gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.07,0:16:53.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1011073,1013450}Killed you, my foot!\NYou two were hugging each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.20,0:16:59.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1017204,1019957}Rina! The Dagger of Yatto\Nhas been stolen!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.83,0:17:06.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1024836,1026880}St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.88,0:17:08.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1026880,1028173}Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.34,0:17:12.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1029341,1032511}I'm sorry, but I'm taking\Nthe dagger with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.35,0:17:23.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1042354,1043564}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.56,0:17:24.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1043564,1044606}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.60,0:17:26.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1044606,1046108}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.27,0:17:29.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1048277,1049194}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.99,0:17:42.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1058996,1062416}Goodbye Mr. Detective.\NIt's been fun, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.87,0:17:49.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1066878,1069548}She did it again, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.54,0:17:51.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1069548,1071967}Damn it! Show me you face!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.96,0:17:53.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1071967,1073927}St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.92,0:17:56.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1073927,1076430}Hey you, what do you think\Nyou're looking at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.05,0:18:00.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1077055,1080392}Thanks to you, I can't see a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.72,0:18:02.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1080726,1082603}Stupid! Stupid!\NSuper Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:03.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1082603,1083854}Who are you calling stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.31,0:18:07.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1084313,1087816}We could've caught her,\Nif you held onto her tighter!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.56,0:18:12.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1088567,1092321}I don't want to have to use\Ntear gas to catch her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.32,0:18:13.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1092321,1093822}What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.82,0:18:15.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1093822,1095449}I'll say this one last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.44,0:18:18.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1095449,1098535}I'm the one who will capture\NSt. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.53,0:18:20.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1098535,1100621}Suit yourself! Humph!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.62,0:18:22.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1100621,1102331}Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.33,0:18:23.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1102331,1103457}Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.43,0:18:43.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1119431,1123518}I left security for this place\Nup to him because he's your son!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.51,0:18:44.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1123518,1124728}I trusted him, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.72,0:18:46.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1124728,1126188}Are you listening to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.18,0:18:48.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1126188,1128398}Do you know how valuable the\NDagger of Yatto is,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.39,0:18:51.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1128398,1131443}both as an archeological\Nand artistic treasure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.44,0:18:54.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1131443,1134071}It's so valuable, that no monetary\Nvalue could be placed on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.07,0:18:57.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1134071,1137032}How are the police going to take\Nresponsibility for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.74,0:19:02.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1137741,1142245}Ah… it's a nice painting.\NDon't tell me this is an imitation, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.33,0:19:04.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1143330,1144247}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.87,0:19:06.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1144873,1146583}I've already investigated.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.58,0:19:12.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1146583,1152464}I hear that your Dagger of Yatto\Nis a genuine replica.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.13,0:19:16.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1153131,1156426}Getting the police involved\Nin your conspiracy…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.42,0:19:19.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1156426,1159179}That's taking it a bit too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.35,0:19:29.31,saint tail sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1165352,1169314}IT WAS A FAKE!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.60,0:19:29.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1165602,1169314}What a stupid thief,\Nstealing a replica.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.89,0:19:33.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1169898,1173026}She ends up stealing for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.31,0:19:35.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1174319,1175570}That's not the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.57,0:19:36.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1175570,1176279}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.03,0:19:40.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1178031,1180075}She knew…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.07,0:19:43.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1180075,1183245}She probably was helping\Nsomebody out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.49,0:19:45.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1183495,1185122}Are you stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.12,0:19:47.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1185122,1187708}And just how would you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.20,0:19:49.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1188208,1189418}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.50,0:19:53.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1190502,1193171}Because I've been chasing\Nher all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.00,0:19:56.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1194005,1196133}Oh, is that so?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.25,0:20:02.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1197259,1202097}St. Tail, I'll reveal your\Ntrue identity!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.81,0:20:10.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1207811,1210230}You were crying last night,\Nweren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.94,0:20:17.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1215944,1217571}How did you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.57,0:20:19.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1217571,1219573}'Cause your eyes are red.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.65,0:20:22.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1220657,1222492}Why did you cry?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.49,0:20:23.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1222492,1223785}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.78,0:20:25.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1223785,1225620}Hey, tell me why.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.66,0:20:28.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1226663,1228874}It's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.75,0:20:31.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1229750,1231585}Men have a lot things to attend to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.54,0:20:39.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1235547,1239551}{\i1}I know, it's because you're always\Ndedicated to the job you 're doing.
